name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of punks are assigned a mysterious mission. These punks are very deadly. They have their own superpowers. Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center. For now, the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #010
Male


Name         : Lrax
Strength     : 76/100
Intelligence : 98/100

According to legends, Lrax created the "Ring of desires" and hid it somewhere in the universe. 
The ring gives the owner the ability to bring desires to reality.
None has found it even after spending lifetime searching for it.
